				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{HO}}^{\cdot}$$\end{document} radicals (ii) they improve the solubility of nonpolar and lipophilic pollutants (iii) they enhance the dissolution of iron at neutral pH and allow the reduction of Fe3+ to Fe2+ using UV light (iv) chelates have the ability to form higher quantum yield from HO·\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
